हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: For ten long years, Shivani's heart beat only for Mohit. A contract marriage and an unexpected child promised a fairytale life — until destiny struck. When Mohit's past returned to claim him, Shivani's world crumbled. Shattered and betrayed, she walked away… only for Mohit to realise, too late, that he had lost the love of a lifetime.
